#  LIBFT4222_INCLUDE_DIRS - the LIBFT4222 include directory
#  LIBFT4222_LIBRARIES - Link these to use LIBFT4222
#  LIBFT4222_DEFINITIONS - Compiler switches required for using LIBFT4222
